{"type": "article", "id": 29838, "title": "模块化壁挂书架", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-19T23:03:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 161, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160719232345AnTEYDOFMd8ZJpzW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>书橱用久了有没有考虑换一种风格？阿根廷著名建筑师及家具设计师 <a href=\"http://sticotti.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alejandro Sticotti</a> 将模块化设计与书架结合在一起，推出了一套灵活度极高的壁挂式书架系统 Sticotti。根据大小及布局，这套壁挂书架共有七种不同的款式，同时提供单片的搁板方便用户自行组合出所需要的造型。和其他模块化家具相比，Sticotti 安装起来更加容易，只需要把搁板沿着插槽插入即可。在材料方面，工作坊仅选用认证过的阿根廷木材，它们全部来自可持续化管理的南美森林，降低对森林的破坏。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1898122422/the-only-bookshelf-you-will-ever-need\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价从 290 到 800 美元不等。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719232359hzUboFLgkqp38HMX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.489645\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719232400i20uyaPj4GdcpzgC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647929\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607192324012rMSk8auWjicRxTz.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762222\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719232402YwT0xjlC9pVvOWc2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762222\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}